         mobilization orders; pay and benefits; and other military career management documents. Resources also increased to add a
         redundancy capability for critical systems to prevent catastrophic loss of operating systems and Sailor OMPF data. (Baseline:
         $10,630)
      iv)Data Center Cloud Migration: Resources increased to migrate the on-premises Charleston Data Center to the Commercial                   5,561
         Cloud to improve efficiency, availability, stability, and cyber security. Due to the interconnectedness of the data and systems,
